omoting Accessibility and Inclusion - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Celebrate International Wheelchair Day: Promoting Accessibility and Inclusion - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-1009_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1010_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by LightFieldStudios via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1012_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Accessibility refers to the design of products, environments, and services that enable people with disabilities to fully participate in all aspects of life. Inclusion, on the other hand, involves creating environments where everyone feels valued, respected, and supported, regardless of their abilities.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1014_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1015_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-1016_">The role of International Wheelchair Day</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/wheelchair-on-the-green-grass-with-outdoors-sunlig-2023-11-27-05-37-05-utc.jpg?v=1710234292" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/wheelchair-on-the-green-grass-with-outdoors-sunlig-2023-11-27-05-37-05-utc.jpg?v=1710234292 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/wheelchair-on-the-green-grass-with-outdoors-sunlig-2023-11-27-05-37-05-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1710234292 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/wheelchair-on-the-green-grass-with-outdoors-sunlig-2023-11-27-05-37-05-utc_500x.jpg?v=1710234292 320w" width="1000" height="668" alt="Accessibility Advocacy: Empowering Wheelchair Users on International Wheelchair Day - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Accessibil